WITH RankedPaintings AS (
  SELECT 
    genre,
    title,
    inception,
    CAST(strftime('%Y', inception) AS INTEGER) AS inception_year,
    (CAST(strftime('%Y', inception) AS INTEGER) - 1) / 100 + 1 AS century,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY genre ORDER BY inception DESC) AS rn
  FROM paintings
  WHERE genre IS NOT NULL AND inception IS NOT NULL
)
SELECT 
  genre,
  title,
  inception_year,
  century
FROM RankedPaintings
WHERE rn = 1
ORDER BY genre
